# Building the container

# build image for VS Code

```bash
hpccm --recipe docker1.py > Dockerfile && cat docker_ext >> Dockerfile
docker build --ssh default -f Dockerfile -t vanreeslab/flups:v1.1 .
docker login
docker push vanreeslab/flups:v1.1
```


